Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古風琴果然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.57,0:00:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經轉移到風華宮地底下了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我原本以為不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但花了幾百年尋找的那個東西\N竟然這麼簡單就找到…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道她們定下契約了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們本人似乎是想隱瞞…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要破除嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話，我很想順其自然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.34,0:00:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者，這可能會\N成為一個契機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想依賴偶然嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也有可能變成必然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果夏樹這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不反對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:00:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去問問看\N在城堡底下到底發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.53,0:01:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現階段最大的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.53,0:01:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個已經響了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該很多地方\N都收到通知了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.82,0:01:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，一切都會開始運轉…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.81,0:01:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心悸動無法平息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿盈內心 開始散放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會如此不安呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法控制的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不禁落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日一定會抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算中途受挫也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能踏出小小的一步 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嶄新的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第8話 命運之軛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是罰掃地也不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是稍微蹺了舞鬥課而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個拿不下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說妳可以休息的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡·夢宮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子餓扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦吧？這裡這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是乙HiME的真祖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二三小姐之墓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是替那個什麼戰爭…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:03:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二王戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劃下休止符的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真白說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡跟真白女王真的很要好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契約？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡跟真白公主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八成是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以那個“蒼天的青玉”進行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她受到Meister GEM的認可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以駕馭它？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮依娜，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳做這種事妳一定很難受…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問問她到底發生什麼事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，愛莉卡的耳環還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有一點發炎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得快點繼續打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔，且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶來的東西還沒給妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是甜點？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更好的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是機械耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是依琳娜做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀，沒什麼了不起的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖先們可是靠著\N科學的力量航行宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到這個星球耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我跑遍廢鐵店和古董店\N還從陽子老師那邊偷…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借用零件之後\N做出來的掃地君1號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按下開關
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害，動了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還冒煙了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著會怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然資料還是不太夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以偷看那道門\N後面的東西就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來想用這個拼過下次\N定期考試的研究發表呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對喔，快到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像幾乎沒有看過妳唸書耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果連續兩學期都最後一名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會退學喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有辦法…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.19,0:06:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全查不到取消契約的方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留姊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，在準備考試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是乖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話要不要我幫妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡真好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然可以接受靜留姊姊的教學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羨慕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說好詐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒聽見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前鎮上傳出好大的聲響呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我完全沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是管風琴聲音之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險好險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點不小心說太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過靜留姊真的好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也是那麼棒的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:07:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了，參考到不少東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像沒有幫上多少忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是妳爸爸的寶貝書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人工智能的書籍相當稀有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能讀過就很夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優每次都突然出現耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧妳知道我在這個學園呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的事情我什麼都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎，晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此，婆婆她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在深優最後一次來的半年後…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園有趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唸書雖然辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的夢想是\N當一個出色的乙HiME嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優一直在旅行對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳有聽說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Meister GEM的契約取消的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實啊，這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳幹嘛突然嚇人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底在混什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃，是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算長這樣\N她可是溫德布倫的女王喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“就算長這樣”這句是多餘的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是說貴石的事情\N是我們的秘密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然對這個\N可疑的流浪漢說這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優不會有問題的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她又不是學園的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且知道很多事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這個得意忘形的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不許妳再侮辱愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這個無禮者是幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我說真白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳為什麼在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是妳一直\N沒找到解除契約的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了溜出來\N可費了一大番功夫耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力在找了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個GEM就是問題關鍵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓我看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister GEM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個很棒的貴石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼做到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管怎麼弄\N都完全拿不下來的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那麼我的這個也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也拿得下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優，妳試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:10:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿…拿下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，總算…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以跟妳斷絕關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說就算貴石拿下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刻在上面的契約仍會保留
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎麼做才能解約啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式向學園請教方法如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話早就做了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們希望這件事情可以保密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溜進禁書庫？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼又要做這麼大膽的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個禁書庫\N不是保存了乙HiME的紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有學園歷史一類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說關於這個星球的歷史\N還有失落的科學等相關書籍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堆得跟寶山一樣多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是被發現可不會好過喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:12:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我想知道關於乙HiME的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說愛莉卡的媽媽\N也是一位乙HiME嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是難得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是為了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來就沒道理不參加了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，具體上該怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊可是挺麻煩的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個點子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點陰森耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是真祖之墓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是在這裡的地下深處長眠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後，愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳先把那個拿下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是婆婆說這個\N是準備做壞事時正確的打扮耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下來就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄出這封情書的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀，真是嚇了我一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為裡面寫著\N要我利用奴獸作戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種程度上來說\N意思或許挺接近的也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面，大公殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，禁書庫的鑰匙\N究竟是怎麼拿到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企業機密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後要好好幫我做兼差工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作就看我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，妳也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個就可以開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可以開這道鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過應該不只這道鎖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前試的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…芝麻開門
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還芝麻開門咧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就靠一句芝麻開門…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡\N妳要是失敗了我可不管妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是禁書庫…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是有書啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是好了不起喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛…愛莉卡妳又做了什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…哪有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起，太了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是資料庫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在移民曆以前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用宇宙船航行過\N許多星球時的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料庫？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點類似非常巨大的圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，這個該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要控制這個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是需要言語或物品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是\N可以當作鑰匙的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想太多了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面好像還有東西喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是什麼地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“流水的透輝石”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister蒙妮卡·尤蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢生奉獻給主人\N卡迪雅王阿格斯12世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自移民曆264年到281年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講到281年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是離現在最近的大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50年前龍王戰爭結束那一年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊的這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墳墓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們都是\N妳們的前輩乙HiME們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們真是做出了\N不得了的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊並不是學生…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，就算王公貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不應該隨便進來的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些全部是…墳墓？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.85,0:17:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙妮卡姊姊，抱歉打擾您了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…妳認識她？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位就是我負責房間的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是一個非常棒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔任三和弦，既高潔又清雅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是當時的世界\N並不像現在這麼安定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸侯渴望霸權
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷重複小規模競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於掀起了那場龍王戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在持續的戰亂之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME們等不到畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一一成為Meister而離校獨立
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在與主人\N訂定的契約之下履行義務
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義務？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME彼此…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而蒙妮卡姊姊打敗的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她學生時代最親近的朋友\N三和弦第二名的那位姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼會這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要打不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能做得到這種事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王的性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為戰爭的勝敗\N委任到乙HiME身上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能夠不荒廢國家\N也不用犧牲人民的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更遑論她們身為乙HiME\N有對主人的尊敬，愛情以及信念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是比友情更強固更尊貴的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好記住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:19:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在人們雖然只看到乙HiME們\N服侍貴族的華美一面就加以崇敬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一旦發生事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是好朋友也要互相廝殺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是身為乙HiME的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們有這樣的覺悟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就離開學園吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡·夢宮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣，不要打仗就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成為夠格的乙HiME之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會阻止戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果做得到這一點\N不知道有多好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們待太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為打擾姊姊們睡眠\N向她們致歉之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就離開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣子對姊姊們太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:19:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛…愛莉卡·夢宮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…那個…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說已經4年\N沒有罰掃外牆過了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過太好了呢，愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好可以拿到新的珊瑚GEM
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過契約還是一籌莫展呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了要幫我打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～愛莉卡～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳打破貴石的事情穿幫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我也挨罵了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都打破了\N還是得想辦法補救啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳果然完全不適合當乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點退學吧，退學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要咧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那種是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會比較重視朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正現在的國際情勢\N跟以前也不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會打仗的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在愛瑞斯境內
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我們去取得那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，時候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不能袖手旁觀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到的東西對半分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是如傳聞所說的貪心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我答應你們的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這份委託
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等黑谷便接下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加迪亞皇帝阿格斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒禮貌，妳收斂點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亞，別急
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人是不順從者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:22:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他們唯一的目標\N就是回歸星球的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.47,0:22:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧？黑谷的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.91,0:22:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是我等黑色山谷的末裔…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.95,0:22:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.88,0:22:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.43,0:23:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來 我想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.78,0:23:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的心意 比寶石更耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.21,0:23:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，幫忙奈緒姊姊是？\N（海－泳裝＋遇難＝？)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.47,0:23:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於…這個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.17,0:23:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.97,0:23:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是單純出賣身體罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身…身體？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.24,0:23:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.71,0:23:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳居然跟這種人相處得來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.58,0:23:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME是清高又正確的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
